== User Stories

* Support creating multi field index from several different node classes.
** Today it only support index on one node class.
** Maybe something like this
   
   index = Index.new(Company => [:name, :employees], [Company, :employees] => [:since], [Company, :employees, Person] => [:name, :age])

   With this information we build an index
   

* Handle corrupt lucene index after a crash
** Find which index is locked in reindex all those

* Compare performance with jdbc and mysql


